<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>fy ẓlmẗ ạllyl</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- fy ẓlmẗ ạllyl fy wḥsẖẗ ḥwly
 lạ ạ̉kẖsẖy̱ mn hwl yạ rb ạ̉nt mʿy
 2- qd lạ try̱ ʿyny sẖkẖṣk bạlʿyn
 lạ zạlt ly ʿwny yạ rb ạ̉nt mʿy
 3- ạ̹dẖ ạ̉nt rạʿy ạ̹dẖ ạ̉nt fạdy
 qlby sẖdy̱ fy yạ rb ạ̉nt mʿy
 4- lạ ạ̉kẖsẖy̱ mn sẖr fy ạlẓlmẗ ysry
 ạ̹dẖ ṭylẗ ạlʿmr yạ rb ạ̉nt mʿy
 5- yạ mn fdy̱ rwḥy tsẖdw lk rwḥy
 fy kl tsbyḥy yạ rb ạ̉nt mʿy</lyrics>
